WEBVTT

1
00:00:04.530 --> 00:00:08.250
Remember Lingling, keep dragging.

2
00:00:14.350 --> 00:00:16.750
Mr. Zou, no, I'm upset.

3
00:00:19.950 --> 00:00:22.290
Remember Lingling, I don't accept that.

4
00:00:22.790 --> 00:00:23.910
Don't be angry at me

5
00:00:23.910 --> 00:00:25.430
when you have a cold.

6
00:00:25.430 --> 00:00:29.430
Ugh, this is so embarrassing and awful!

7
